OL,3,CPolice told to scale back arrests in
OL,4,Cbid to cut prison overcrowding ` report
OL,6,FPolice are reportedly being advised to
OL,7,Farrest fewer people in a bid to ease
OL,8,Fovercrowding in prisons.
OL,10,FForce chiefs are being told to
OL,11,Fconsider halting "non-priority
OL,12,Farrests" until there is capacity in
OL,13,FEngland and Wales's jails, The Times
OL,14,Freported.
