OL,4,Cbid to cut prison overcrowding ` report
OL,6,FThe newspaper said it obtained an
OL,7,Finternal document from the National
OL,8,FPolice Chiefs' Council (NPCC) which
OL,9,Falso said "any planned operations
OL,10,Fwhere large numbers of arrests may
OL,11,Ftake place" should potentially be
OL,12,Fpaused to ease pressures in the
OL,13,Fcriminal justice system.
OL,15,FThis is thought to apply to operations
OL,16,Fthat do not have to happen on a
OL,17,Fspecific date and could be arranged
OL,18,Ffor a later time.
