OL,3,CPolice told to scale back arrests in
OL,4,Cbid to cut prison overcrowding ` report
OL,6,FThe news is likely to heap pressure on
OL,7,FRishi Sunak's Government, which has
OL,8,Frecently come under fire over a policy
OL,9,Fto free criminals from jail early and
OL,10,Fdelays to court cases as part of
OL,11,Fefforts to cut prison overcrowding.
OL,13,FFirst announced last year, the
OL,14,FGovernment insisted the early release
OL,15,Fscheme would be temporary and would
OL,16,Fonly allow "low-level offenders" out
OL,17,Fof prison up to 18 days early under
OL,18,Fstrict supervision.
