OL,6,FBut earlier this month, it emerged
OL,7,Fthat ministers were preparing to
OL,8,Fextend the scheme for a second time so
OL,9,Fsome criminals could be freed from
OL,10,Fjail up to 70 days before their
OL,11,Frelease date. This is expected to take
OL,12,Feffect from Thursday.
OL,14,FLabour said the Tories'
OL,15,F"mismanagement" of the criminal
OL,16,Fjustice system "cannot go on".
