OL,3,CPolice told to scale back arrests in
OL,4,Cbid to cut prison overcrowding ` report
OL,6,FA separate, internal letter from the
OL,7,FNPCC to chief constables in England
OL,8,Fand Wales, seen by The Times, warned
OL,9,Fthat the Government's contingency
OL,10,Fmeasures are having an "unsustainable
OL,11,Foperational impact on policing", risk
OL,12,Fpublic safety and could limit
OL,13,Fofficers' ability to investigate crime.
OL,15,FThe paper said the memo also warned of
OL,16,Fthe risk of suspects suing police
OL,17,Fforces for unlawful detention due to
OL,18,Fthe knock-on effects of the Ministry
OL,19,Fof Justice's so-called Operation Early
OL,20,FDawn.
