OL,6,FThe measure allows defendants to be
OL,7,Fheld in police cells ` and not be
OL,8,Ftransferred to magistrates' courts for
OL,9,Fbail hearings ` until prison beds
OL,10,Fbecome available.
OL,12,FLabour's shadow justice secretary
OL,13,FShabana Mahmood said: "It beggars
OL,14,Fbelief that police are being told to
OL,15,Fsit on their hands and ignore crime
OL,16,Fbecause the Conservatives have
OL,17,Fmismanaged the criminal justice system
OL,18,Fso badly.
